<HEADLINE> Sullivan County boy killed by sports utility vehicle at fair  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	   GRAHAMSVILLE, N.Y. (AP) - A 7-year-old Sullivan County boy died
after being struck by a sports utility vehicle at a nearby fair.
</P>
