Dow Ends Up 33, Nasdaq Gains 23
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks closed higher today on optimism that the Federal
Reserve Board will leave interest rates alone tomorrow. The Dow Jones industrial
average closed up 33.33 at 11,079.81. Broader stock indicators were also higher.
The Nasdaq composite index was up 22.81 at 3,953.15.
</P>
