on Sunday made him the third Phillies pitcher to throw a shutout
this season. The last time they had three pitchers throw a shutout
was 1993. ... Bobby Abreu, who batted leadoff for the first time in
his career Sunday and went 2-for-3, hit leadoff again Monday. ...
Scott Rolen was in an 0-for-15 slump. ... Travis Lee is a .143
career hitter at Cinergy Field (6-for-42).
